HOW TO PLAY WORDLE GAME ?
1.You will have six tries to guess the five letter wordle of the day.
2.Type your guess word and submit your word by clicking the enter key on the wordle keyboard.
3.The colour of the tile will change after you submit your word.
  1).a yellow colour tile indicates that you have picked the correct letter but it is not in correct spot.
  2).a green colour tile indicates that you have picked the correct letter in the correct spot.
  3).a cyan colour tile indicates that you have picked letter is not included in the word at all.
4.Continue until you solve the word or run out of guesses.
